	- var page = 'work'

block content
	
	.uk-section.uk-section-large
		.uk-container.uk-container-small.uk-margin-large
			h1 #{title}
			p.uk-text-lead
				| We've been producing top quality, user driven applications for dozens of clients, for over 7 years. From one person startups, to leading enterprises, universities and non-profits. Here is a sample of some of our recent work.
	.uk-section.uk-section-large.uk-section-primary.uk-preserve-color
		.uk-container
			div(class="uk-child-width-1-2@s uk-child-width-1-3@m uk-grid-medium uk-grid-match" uk-grid uk-scrollspy="cls: uk-animation-fade; target: .uk-card; delay: 150;")
